OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,FParalympian Baroness Tanni Grey-
OL,7,FThompson has said no disabled person
OL,8,Fwho uses public transport would be
OL,9,Fsurprised by the findings in a damning
OL,10,Freport published by the Commons'
OL,11,FTransport Select Committee on Thursday.
OL,13,FIt found "far too great a burden" is
OL,14,Fplaced on individual disabled people
OL,15,Fto hold operators and authorities to
OL,16,Faccount for not fulfilling their
OL,17,Fduties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
