OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,F"When anyone from a train company asks
OL,7,Ffor what I want... what I say is that
OL,8,FI just want the same experience of
OL,9,Fcommuting as everyone else," Grey-
OL,10,FThompson said.
OL,12,FThe report said the evidence shows
OL,13,Fthere is still "a very substantial
OL,14,Fgap" between "the rights and
OL,15,Fobligations that exist in theory", and
OL,16,F"the daily experience of people who
OL,17,Frely on pavements, buses, taxis,
OL,18,Ftrains and planes to get to work, to
OL,19,Faccess services or for leisure".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
