OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,FThat daily difficulty when it comes to
OL,7,Ftransport is something with which
OL,8,Fdisability rights campaigner Doug
OL,9,FPaulley is all too familiar.
OL,11,F"Accessibility feels like it's going
OL,12,Fbackwards," he said, as he listed the
OL,13,Fmodes of transport he's struggled with
OL,14,Fin the past.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
