OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,F"I've been refused access in taxis
OL,7,Fbecause they don't want to take my
OL,8,Fwheelchair or they've forgotten their
OL,9,Framp, I've had multiple occasions
OL,10,Fwhere I've not been able to catch
OL,11,Fbuses because the wheelchair spaces
OL,12,Fhave been occupied by non-disabled
OL,13,Fpeople and I haven't wanted to do
OL,14,Fanything about it... I've been left on
OL,15,Fplanes because I've had to wait for a
OL,16,Flong time for them to come to get me
OL,17,Foff - these are all very familiar to
OL,18,Fme unfortunately," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
