OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,FFrom Harrow-on-the-Hill to King's
OL,7,FCross there are 14 stations and only a
OL,8,Fcouple are accessible, which Mr Gabsi
OL,9,Fsaid: "Is a reflection of the London
OL,10,FUnderground system generally".
OL,12,F"Some people don't travel due to
OL,13,Fconcerns with regards to emergencies,
OL,14,Ffire safety, general planning... And
OL,15,Feven though (at some stations) the
OL,16,Ftrain is accessible, you can't get out
OL,17,Fof the station. That's a big barrier,"
OL,18,Fhe added.
