OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,FRuth Cadbury, who chairs the Transport
OL,7,FCommittee, went as far as to describe
OL,8,Fthe issue as a "source of national
OL,9,Fembarrassment".
OL,11,F"Our country's transport services
OL,12,Feffectively treat disabled people as
OL,13,Fsecond-class citizens, denying them
OL,14,Faccess to jobs, leisure, support
OL,15,Fnetworks and essential services `
OL,16,Fdenying them their rights."
