OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,FShe continued: "Those who have been
OL,7,Flet down and want redress or
OL,8,Fcompensation face a spaghetti junction
OL,9,Fof complaints processes that either
OL,10,Ffobs them off or leads them on a road
OL,11,Fto nowhere."
OL,13,F"Failures must go from being an
OL,14,Feveryday occurrence to vanishingly
OL,15,Frare."
OL,17,FGrey-Thompson said she hopes the
OL,18,Freport "highlights the issue and wakes
OL,19,Fup the wider industry".
