OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,F"They can't let this keep going on.
OL,7,FTrains were meant to be step-free by
OL,8,FJanuary 1, 2020 under the Disability
OL,9,FDiscrimination Act, and every single
OL,10,Fgovernment since then has kicked the
OL,11,Fcan down the road and it's now going
OL,12,Fto be a hundred years before trains
OL,13,Fare step-free," Grey-Thompson she
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FThe report gave a list of
OL,17,Frecommendations, including:
