OL,6,FIn response to the report, Local
OL,7,FTransport Minister Simon Lightwood
OL,8,Ftold ITV News it was "clear" that
OL,9,Faccessibility "has been an
OL,10,Fafterthought" in developing transport
OL,11,Fservices, and that "there is more to
OL,12,Fdo to ensure everyone can travel
OL,13,Feasily and with dignity".
