OL,3,CTanni Grey-Thompson 'not surprised' by
OL,4,Cdamning disabled transport report
OL,6,F"That's why we have clear ambitions
OL,7,Ffor a transport network that works for
OL,8,Fall and have already worked quickly to
OL,9,Fput accessibility at the heart of our
OL,10,Fbus and rail reforms, as well as
OL,11,Fcontinuing work to make hundreds of
OL,12,Ftrain stations step-free and launched
OL,13,Fan accessible aviation expert group,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"We continue to work closely with a
OL,17,Frange of people, including disabled
OL,18,Fpeople, to help us develop our
OL,19,Fpolicies, and we will consider these
OL,20,Frecommendations carefully as respond
OL,21,Fas soon as possible."
